Name: Mallard feather
Description: With shades of green and brown, she is quite beautiful.

DescriptionLocalization.es: Con tonos de verde y marrón, es bastante hermosa.
DescriptionLocalization.ko: 녹색과 갈색 음영으로 그녀는 매우 아름답습니다.
DescriptionLocalization.de: Mit Grün- und Brauntönen ist sie ziemlich schön.
DescriptionLocalization.fr: Avec des nuances de vert et de marron, elle est plutôt belle.
DescriptionLocalization.hu: A zöld és barna árnyalataival nagyon szép.
DescriptionLocalization.it: Con sfumature di verde e marrone, è piuttosto bella.
DescriptionLocalization.ja: 緑と茶色の色合いで、彼女はとても美しいです。
DescriptionLocalization.pt: Com tons de marrom, ela é bastante lustrosa.
DescriptionLocalization.ru: С оттенками зеленого и коричневого она довольно красива.
DescriptionLocalization.tr: Yeşil ve kahverengi tonlarıyla oldukça güzel.
DescriptionLocalization.zh: 绿色和棕色的色调，她很漂亮。
